data.title: Register for the Q1 2024 NorCal NUG San Francisco Meeting
data.meta_description: The Q1 2024 NorCal NUG Meeting in San Francisco - Join us for classroom learning, networking, and a happy hour on Thursday, March 14th in Union Square.
data.text:
The Northern California NetSuite User Group

Q1 Meeting

~ San Francisco ~

Thursday, March 14th

3:00pm - Union Square

For our first event of 2024, we're trying something new.

Classroom learning and a happy-hour too!

@ Industrious Union Square

& Iron Horse Cocktail Lounge

Scroll down the page for complete event details

including information about our agenda, speakers, venues, and sponsors.

NUGCommunity.org is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. We use the information gathered in this form in the administration of our live events. This information will be shared with our event sponsors.

By clicking "Register Now" above, you consent to allow NetSuite User Groups by Business Solution Partners to store and process the personal information submitted above to create a reservation and deliver follow-up emails with the details of the event.

Shannon Moffett

Host - NorCal NUG

Shannon Moffett is the host and administrative manager of the NorCal NetSuite User Group. She works for the founding partner of the NorCal NUG - Business Solution Partners - in the capacity of Community and Events Manager. She also oversees NetSuite User Groups in SoCal, the New York Metro Area and Austin, Texas. A former employee of Oracle NetSuite in the Account Management role, Shannon brings a wealth of NetSuite knowledge and hard-won insights to share with our community.

Aaron Shreve

PRATCTUCE MANAGER - NETSUTIE EDUCATION

Aaron works every day to improve NetSuite's client experience through education. You have likely seen him at NetSuite Learning Labs and at our own User Group Meetings! We are so happy to welcome him back!
